WEBVTT

02:03.250 --> 02:04.833
Topsy Turvy.

02:11.958 --> 02:14.125
We’re both hard-headed.

02:35.208 --> 02:40.208
It’s your first day at school
and that’s what you’re wearing? Go change!

03:27.375 --> 03:29.375
No music when we’re at the table!

03:35.041 --> 03:35.875
See you, bitch.

03:37.833 --> 03:38.750
Right back at you!

04:12.041 --> 04:15.666
FEEL MY VOICE

05:05.541 --> 05:07.500
<i>…the most beautiful in the world</i>

05:08.208 --> 05:11.708
<i>And your eyes are the most sincere</i>

05:13.125 --> 05:17.125
<i>And in my heart lies a true love</i>

05:18.083 --> 05:23.291
<i>Since the day you were born</i>

08:43.625 --> 08:44.833
What are you doing?!

09:01.208 --> 09:02.291
We wanted to do you a favor.

09:02.375 --> 09:03.291
You didn’t sleep last night.

09:48.666 --> 09:49.791
It greases up my underwear.

09:51.208 --> 09:53.416
And the donkeys like it.

09:55.208 --> 10:00.791
The other day, Osvaldo tried
to nip my balls.

10:21.166 --> 10:22.291
For how long?

10:26.083 --> 10:27.041
Forget it!

14:22.250 --> 14:25.041
What the fuck?
Why did you close the door?

14:32.250 --> 14:34.541
Tell her she’s very pretty.

14:40.666 --> 14:41.958
What did she say?

15:30.875 --> 15:32.583
Is your boyfriend here?

15:33.875 --> 15:35.166
Then turn the light off!

15:37.166 --> 15:38.125
Again?

16:08.125 --> 16:10.583
At last, you brought a friend!

16:16.750 --> 16:18.750
Why did she say I’m a wanker?

18:28.958 --> 18:30.791
Tell them to fuck off!

18:41.625 --> 18:43.625
Don’t get upset and smile!

22:36.041 --> 22:37.625
WE DON’T NEED WORDS

23:09.083 --> 23:10.833
<i>Now come here</i>…

23:14.583 --> 23:15.666
What were you doing?

23:20.166 --> 23:22.291
The mayor is live. It’s a TV special.

23:50.916 --> 23:52.791
That asshole!

23:54.291 --> 23:56.458
I’ll run in the election.

23:57.500 --> 23:59.250
We’ll all work together!

23:59.333 --> 24:00.583
I’m in.

24:27.416 --> 24:28.333
Why?

24:32.333 --> 24:33.958
Because I’m Deaf?

24:38.625 --> 24:41.666
You know very well that being Deaf means
having an identity and a culture.

24:48.666 --> 24:51.416
Do you want me to let that idiot
destroy everything?

25:03.375 --> 25:06.541
You know the farm is our life.

25:07.666 --> 25:10.666
Everyone wants money.

25:11.916 --> 25:15.458
But not us. We take care of animals.

25:17.583 --> 25:21.125
Even if they speak a different language
than ours, they understand us.

25:26.791 --> 25:29.291
So, what about Elon Musk?

25:30.416 --> 25:33.583
He has Asperger’s Syndrome.

25:33.666 --> 25:35.958
And yet, he’s headed to Mars!

25:36.041 --> 25:38.458
And he’s the richest man in the world!

25:40.083 --> 25:44.750
Remember. Changing things
requires thinking differently.

25:45.333 --> 25:46.625
That’s important!

26:00.125 --> 26:01.208
Me, more.

26:02.166 --> 26:05.708
Even if you are flawed.

26:13.208 --> 26:14.500
You’re too serious!

26:44.375 --> 26:46.083
I DON’T HEAR EXCUSES

26:52.708 --> 26:54.375
I CAN’T HEAR YOU,
BUT I SEE YOU

27:03.250 --> 27:04.250
I CAN’T HEAR BULLSHIT

27:10.708 --> 27:12.958
Vote for me!

27:14.916 --> 27:15.833
I LISTEN TO YOU

27:43.416 --> 27:45.291
<i>Now come here</i>

27:47.958 --> 27:51.250
<i>And gently close your eyes</i>

27:54.208 --> 27:57.208
<i>You’ll see that the sadness will go away</i>

27:58.791 --> 28:00.500
<i>And as for the rest, who knows</i>

28:01.291 --> 28:02.291
<i>It will come tomorrow</i>

28:08.166 --> 28:09.958
<i>I want to be with </i>you

28:45.750 --> 28:47.541
<i>Now come here</i>

28:50.375 --> 28:53.583
<i>And gently close your eyes</i>

28:56.666 --> 28:59.708
<i>You’ll see that the sadness will go away</i>

29:01.208 --> 29:02.833
<i>And as for the rest, who knows</i>

29:03.500 --> 29:04.791
<i>It will come tomorrow</i>

29:10.583 --> 29:12.291
<i>I want to be with </i>you

29:15.000 --> 29:18.416
<i>Kiss your lips and tell you that</i>

29:21.166 --> 29:24.541
<i>In a time when everything passes</i>

29:25.916 --> 29:27.708
<i>Where everything changes</i>

29:28.208 --> 29:30.250
<i>We are still here</i>

32:32.333 --> 32:33.958
<i>Now come here</i>

32:36.958 --> 32:40.291
<i>And gently close your eyes</i>

32:43.208 --> 32:46.208
<i>You’ll see that the sadness will go away</i>

32:47.750 --> 32:49.208
<i>And as for the rest, who knows</i>

32:50.250 --> 32:51.208
<i>It will come tomorrow</i>

32:57.083 --> 32:59.000
<i>I want to be with </i>you

33:01.541 --> 33:04.958
<i>Kiss your lips and tell you that</i>

33:07.791 --> 33:11.291
<i>In a time when everything passes</i>

33:12.416 --> 33:14.250
<i>Where everything changes</i>

33:14.916 --> 33:16.625
<i>We are still here</i>

33:18.541 --> 33:22.041
<i>And we don’t need words</i>

33:22.791 --> 33:28.083
<i>To explain what is hidden</i>
<i>Deep in our hearts</i>

33:29.250 --> 33:34.500
<i>But I will lift you up every time you fall</i>

33:35.250 --> 33:37.500
<i>And I will pick up your flowers…</i>

34:25.291 --> 34:27.083
<i>Now come here</i>

34:30.416 --> 34:33.916
<i>And gently close your eyes</i>

34:36.541 --> 34:39.750
<i>You’ll see that the sadness will go away</i>

34:41.166 --> 34:42.875
<i>And as for the rest, who knows</i>

34:43.666 --> 34:44.750
<i>It will come tomorrow</i>

34:47.333 --> 34:49.166
<i>I want to be with </i>you

34:51.833 --> 34:55.250
<i>Kiss your lips and tell you that</i>

34:57.958 --> 35:01.333
<i>In a time when everything passes</i>

35:02.583 --> 35:04.208
<i>Where everything changes</i>

35:05.458 --> 35:07.333
<i>We are still here</i>

35:18.875 --> 35:23.916
It was a joke! I thought you were
alone. You usually laugh!

35:30.666 --> 35:33.208
You brought your boyfriend.
He’s really hot!

35:33.291 --> 35:35.625
I’m happy!

35:35.708 --> 35:37.791
He’s not my boyfriend!

35:37.875 --> 35:41.458
Earlier, upstairs, I heard some noises…

35:44.500 --> 35:47.458
He’s muscular. Perfect for farming!

35:48.875 --> 35:51.000
Did you fuck my sister?

35:51.083 --> 35:51.958
I’m watching you!

35:52.791 --> 35:55.208
If you get her pregnant, I’ll take it

35:55.291 --> 35:57.791
and slice it into pieces!

41:06.750 --> 41:08.166
He’ll shove it up your ass!

41:59.875 --> 42:02.125
That’s great news! Why the frown?

42:08.125 --> 42:10.291
Stop it! We’re Deaf, not stupid.

42:10.541 --> 42:14.000
Before you were born, we got by just fine.

42:15.625 --> 42:16.500
So?

42:17.000 --> 42:19.833
If you weren’t always in the way,

42:19.916 --> 42:22.166
I’d have already completed my project!

42:27.333 --> 42:29.333
I have a dream.

42:29.416 --> 42:32.291
To turn this place
into an educational farm

42:32.375 --> 42:34.375
and rent out rooms!

42:39.583 --> 42:40.958
Because you underestimate me!

42:41.041 --> 42:43.750
I studied agriculture for a reason.

42:45.541 --> 42:47.208
But do you truly want to sing?

42:50.291 --> 42:51.875
Not, maybe. It’s either yes or no!

42:53.875 --> 42:56.291
Then do it! And don’t bust my balls!

43:09.375 --> 43:10.666
I have an idea!

43:12.125 --> 43:15.208
Martina can replace you at the market.
I’ll teach her sign language!

49:00.708 --> 49:01.833
Where are you going?

49:03.166 --> 49:05.750
The TV people are about to arrive.

49:08.583 --> 49:10.583
I thought Dad had told you.

49:12.666 --> 49:14.041
Impossible!

49:20.541 --> 49:21.833
Ah, your boyfriend!

49:21.916 --> 49:24.958
Get him to come here!
He’s part of the family, now.

49:28.083 --> 49:29.583
You can do them here.

49:29.666 --> 49:32.500
He’ll be proud to see
his father-in-law become mayor!

49:58.041 --> 50:00.000
Who is she?

50:31.916 --> 50:35.083
Sorry, but is she from the TV?

50:54.375 --> 50:56.416
Camagna is a town of 500 residents.

50:58.291 --> 51:00.666
So far, we have farmed the land
and raised animals.

51:04.416 --> 51:06.791
Today, someone wants to intervene.

51:06.875 --> 51:08.541
HELLO GIULIANA. I CONFIRM THAT I WILL BE
AT THE LESSON THIS AFTERNOON

51:08.625 --> 51:12.166
They say that our produce isn’t
sufficient. That we can produce more

51:12.250 --> 51:14.250
to reach the global market.

51:15.791 --> 51:17.583
I’M SORRY, I’LL BE LATE TONIGHT…

51:18.416 --> 51:19.708
You can already feel the smog,

51:19.791 --> 51:22.583
and everything is moving faster.

51:42.791 --> 51:44.375
Handicap? How dare you?

51:47.500 --> 51:49.458
And you, with that setup?
Do you think you’re a journalist?

51:54.041 --> 51:56.458
If you’re a journalist, I can be mayor!

52:01.083 --> 52:02.875
GET HERE IN HALF AN HOUR
OR YOU CAN STAY WHERE YOU ARE

52:02.958 --> 52:04.000
IT’S NOT UP TO ME

52:11.958 --> 52:13.083
Did you translate?

52:13.166 --> 52:14.416
I’m translating like always!

52:14.916 --> 52:16.958
Are you sure you translated?
You’ve got your face in your phone…

52:18.625 --> 52:20.041
Who are you texting?

52:21.791 --> 52:23.791
Your behavior’s not appropriate.

52:24.583 --> 52:27.250
I missed my date with my boyfriend.

52:27.333 --> 52:30.250
Everything always
has to revolve around you!

52:30.333 --> 52:32.333
And you don’t care about my life.

52:32.833 --> 52:34.833
What’s that got to do with anything?

52:38.625 --> 52:42.291
Translate properly now, word for word.

52:42.375 --> 52:43.791
Translate!

52:43.875 --> 52:45.583
Look at me.

55:33.625 --> 55:36.041
You were terrible!

55:37.500 --> 55:39.250
Apologize to your father.

55:43.458 --> 55:45.666
You’re not the only girl
in the world with a boyfriend.

55:45.750 --> 55:50.000
There are lots like you. But remember that
you have responsibilities.

55:50.083 --> 55:52.375
Your boyfriend comes after them.

55:52.458 --> 55:53.458
Apologize!

56:13.750 --> 56:14.791
Are you pregnant?

56:46.375 --> 56:48.625
You really want to move to Turin?

56:50.916 --> 56:53.083
So you won’t be at home with us anymore?

56:56.500 --> 56:58.375
How long have you been singing?

57:09.000 --> 57:11.000
What’s this teacher’s name?

57:12.791 --> 57:13.708
And her last name?

57:14.625 --> 57:18.625
Her last name is Dickhead!
She’s brainwashed you!

57:19.458 --> 57:22.666
Don’t you have anything to say?

57:30.458 --> 57:32.041
Ah, I get it.

57:36.791 --> 57:38.791
You set it all up.

57:38.875 --> 57:41.791
You figured it all out in secret.

57:43.791 --> 57:47.583
No, Mom. It’s not like that.
She wanted to tell you sooner.

57:47.666 --> 57:49.916
You are the problem.

57:53.583 --> 57:56.541
So, that means we’re the problem?

58:05.125 --> 58:06.291
I’m here too!

58:07.208 --> 58:10.708
You’ve always told me
we Deaf people are better than others.

58:10.791 --> 58:12.541
But actually you two

58:12.625 --> 58:15.375
have never had faith in me!

58:15.458 --> 58:18.541
You should be ashamed!

58:19.541 --> 58:21.541
I can stand up for myself!

58:34.125 --> 58:35.458
Say something to her!

58:36.250 --> 58:38.916
I’m beat. I’m going to bed.

58:50.166 --> 58:53.000
Are you happy? See what you’ve done?

59:27.833 --> 59:31.208
Our daughter wants to be a singer,
and you’re just standing there!

59:32.041 --> 59:34.583
If she wants to be a singer,
we should let her.

59:34.666 --> 59:38.375
So she can show her ass
to the whole world.

59:38.458 --> 59:42.333
Since when have you been such a bigot?

59:43.250 --> 59:45.791
Don’t you understand, she’s in danger?

59:45.875 --> 59:48.125
And you’re just there…

59:48.750 --> 59:51.583
You have to tell her to stay here.

59:52.500 --> 59:54.958
What if she doesn’t have
a beautiful voice?

59:55.041 --> 59:58.250
It’s that Giuliana who put that idea
in her head!

59:59.708 --> 01:00:03.916
Stop being silly, enough!
Stop talking nonsense!

01:00:04.416 --> 01:00:06.583
Our daughter isn’t stupid.

01:00:07.375 --> 01:00:10.125
You’re the one with issues.

01:00:10.208 --> 01:00:13.166
Okay. Let’s say she gets in.

01:00:13.250 --> 01:00:15.375
How do we manage here?

01:00:15.458 --> 01:00:18.625
Oh, so the problem isn’t that
our daughter is going to Turin.

01:00:18.708 --> 01:00:21.500
But that the two of us will be here alone.

01:00:24.750 --> 01:00:26.333
Come here.

01:00:27.875 --> 01:00:29.250
Look at me!

01:00:32.125 --> 01:00:35.125
I’m sure that Eletta will miss us…

01:00:36.000 --> 01:00:37.458
and come back.

01:00:39.083 --> 01:00:43.083
Please, tell her to stay.

01:00:44.708 --> 01:00:46.708
Of course.

01:02:01.041 --> 01:02:03.625
<i>There is a reason growing in </i>me

01:02:05.416 --> 01:02:07.666
<i>And my naivety’s fading</i>

01:02:09.583 --> 01:02:10.875
<i>And like a journey…</i>

01:02:19.041 --> 01:02:21.708
<i>…in the night, it ends</i>

01:02:21.791 --> 01:02:24.958
<i>Tell me, tell me, tell me</i>
<i>What sense it makes</i>

01:02:26.000 --> 01:02:29.166
<i>To give love to a man who has no mercy</i>

01:02:30.791 --> 01:02:34.000
<i>One who never felt defeated</i>

01:02:34.083 --> 01:02:37.291
<i>Who never lost, never</i>

01:02:37.375 --> 01:02:40.291
<i>For you, for you…</i>

01:03:51.166 --> 01:03:52.041
Zero!

01:03:54.416 --> 01:03:57.375
I don’t sell anymore, I don’t fuck anymore, and I beat people up.

01:04:00.875 --> 01:04:02.708
It’s your fault!

01:04:04.208 --> 01:04:05.750
Martina’s a disaster.

01:04:07.708 --> 01:04:09.583
She has to be kind, she’s not polite!

01:05:50.875 --> 01:05:52.291
<i>I’d like</i>

01:05:53.916 --> 01:05:57.458
<i>To give you my word</i>
<i>To tell you I can’t wait</i>

01:05:57.750 --> 01:06:00.041
<i>To forget everything</i>

01:06:00.958 --> 01:06:02.083
<i>I’d like…</i>

01:07:02.625 --> 01:07:05.500
Tomorrow at 6 p.m.,
we have a meeting with the voters.

01:07:05.583 --> 01:07:08.958
Mom’s asked Giacinto to give us a hand.

01:07:12.541 --> 01:07:15.708
We need to get by on our own from now on.

01:07:16.958 --> 01:07:17.833
Of course.

01:07:24.458 --> 01:07:27.250
HOW LONG WILL YOU BE AWAY FROM SCHOOL?

01:07:27.333 --> 01:07:31.708
MARCO: TWO MONTHS I THINK.
IF I BEHAVE MAYBE LESS

01:07:37.000 --> 01:07:39.250
THEN BEHAVE. SO YOU CAN KEEP SINGING

01:07:39.333 --> 01:07:42.291
YOU’RE OBSESSED WITH SINGING

01:07:48.833 --> 01:07:51.458
YES. SINGING MAKES ME FEEL GOOD.
I DISCOVERED THAT WITH YOU.

01:07:51.541 --> 01:07:54.958
THEN SING AS MUCH AS YOU CAN

01:08:00.750 --> 01:08:03.291
<i>There is a reason growing in </i>me

01:08:04.666 --> 01:08:07.041
<i>And my naivety’s fading</i>

01:08:08.791 --> 01:08:12.291
<i>And like a journey in the night, it ends</i>

01:08:12.375 --> 01:08:15.000
<i>Tell me, tell me, tell me</i>
<i>What sense it makes</i>

01:08:16.250 --> 01:08:18.958
<i>To give love to a man who has no mercy</i>

01:08:20.791 --> 01:08:26.833
<i>One who never felt defeated</i>
<i>Who never lost, never</i>

01:08:26.916 --> 01:08:33.291
<i>For you, for you a song</i>

01:08:34.708 --> 01:08:41.583
<i>Never a cheap illusion, a banal thought</i>
<i>Something that remains</i>

01:08:41.666 --> 01:08:48.666
<i>Instead, for me, for me</i>
<i>It’s more than normal</i>

01:08:50.416 --> 01:08:55.083
<i>That such a slight emotion</i>
<i>Can make me feel this </i>bad

01:08:55.166 --> 01:08:58.625
<i>One softly-spoken word is enough</i>

01:08:58.708 --> 01:09:02.000
<i>And I can no longer see reality</i>

01:09:02.458 --> 01:09:05.500
<i>I don’t know where it is anymore</i>

01:09:06.291 --> 01:09:09.291
<i>The clear difference</i>

01:09:09.375 --> 01:09:13.875
<i>Between the blindest love</i>
<i>And the stupidest patience</i>

01:09:13.958 --> 01:09:20.916
<i>No, I can no longer see reality</i>
<i>Nor how much tenderness it gives </i>you

01:09:21.833 --> 01:09:24.666
<i>My incoherence</i>

01:09:24.791 --> 01:09:29.250
<i>Thinking that you would live</i>
<i>Just fine without</i>

01:09:44.000 --> 01:09:46.291
Let them go sing, the young people!

01:10:20.875 --> 01:10:22.625
You scared me.

01:10:22.708 --> 01:10:24.166
You want to see me dead?

01:10:27.666 --> 01:10:30.250
Who introduced him to Martina?
It’s your fault!

01:10:31.583 --> 01:10:34.666
And you, what are you doing
while you’re driving?

01:10:41.916 --> 01:10:43.333
You’re a little girl…

01:10:55.666 --> 01:10:57.291
All traitors!

01:11:00.083 --> 01:11:02.166
No. I’m talking about you.

01:11:02.250 --> 01:11:04.500
You left me there on my own.

01:11:12.125 --> 01:11:12.958
And Mom?

01:11:33.000 --> 01:11:34.916
Leave me alone. Don’t touch me.

01:11:35.000 --> 01:11:38.000
Leave me alone! Here, with the cheese.

01:11:40.333 --> 01:11:41.833
I want to stay here!

01:11:44.791 --> 01:11:48.250
Help me? But I’m a terrible mother.

01:11:52.375 --> 01:11:54.833
Because I’m Deaf,

01:11:54.916 --> 01:11:57.500
and I couldn’t find
the right words with you!

01:12:11.666 --> 01:12:16.833
When you were born,
and they told me

01:12:18.666 --> 01:12:21.750
that you could hear, I cried.

01:12:22.250 --> 01:12:24.250
Those like you,

01:12:24.333 --> 01:12:27.250
I could never stand them!

01:12:29.375 --> 01:12:34.166
But he calmed me down saying

01:12:34.625 --> 01:12:39.458
he would have raised you Deaf inside.

01:12:40.083 --> 01:12:44.625
But, instead, you can hear.

01:12:45.666 --> 01:12:53.208
And you want to go away to sing.

01:13:22.666 --> 01:13:24.666
There is no problem.

01:13:25.625 --> 01:13:27.541
It’s better if you go.

01:13:28.041 --> 01:13:30.166
Follow your own path. You’re free.

01:13:33.541 --> 01:13:35.041
We’ll get by on our own.

01:15:29.375 --> 01:15:31.083
Shall we go to the hair salon?

01:15:44.166 --> 01:15:45.875
Why not give it a try like that for once?

01:16:09.125 --> 01:16:11.791
This is Giuliana, my teacher!

01:16:15.250 --> 01:16:18.166
This woman is a nightmare!

01:16:20.000 --> 01:16:21.416
I’d like to slap her!

01:16:23.666 --> 01:16:24.833
Stay away from my daughter!

01:16:30.916 --> 01:16:32.416
What she thinks of you?

01:16:32.500 --> 01:16:36.125
I already know my daughter. I raised her.

01:16:54.166 --> 01:16:56.833
What do you know?
You’ve never had children.

01:20:43.125 --> 01:20:44.833
<i>Now come here</i>

01:20:47.750 --> 01:20:51.166
<i>And gently close your eyes</i>

01:20:53.958 --> 01:20:57.166
<i>You’ll see that the sadness will go away</i>

01:20:58.458 --> 01:21:01.708
<i>And the rest, who knows</i>
<i>It will come tomorrow</i>

01:21:07.833 --> 01:21:09.625
<i>I want to be with </i>you

01:21:12.375 --> 01:21:15.708
<i>Kiss your lips and tell you that</i>

01:21:18.666 --> 01:21:21.875
<i>In a time when everything passes</i>

01:21:22.958 --> 01:21:24.708
<i>Where everything changes</i>

01:21:25.375 --> 01:21:27.208
<i>We are still here</i>

01:21:29.250 --> 01:21:35.666
<i>And we don’t need words</i>
<i>To explain what </i>is…

01:22:21.750 --> 01:22:26.291
<i>I will follow your flight</i>
<i>Without ever interfering</i>

01:22:28.791 --> 01:22:33.958
<i>Because all I want is to be with </i>you

01:22:35.458 --> 01:22:39.916
<i>Without chains, to be with…</i>

01:22:40.625 --> 01:22:41.916
You

01:24:26.000 --> 01:24:27.375
She learned our language.

01:24:43.166 --> 01:24:45.375
The show was fantastic.

01:24:45.458 --> 01:24:47.458
Eletta moved everybody. My compliments.

01:24:53.416 --> 01:24:57.000
The staging was great,
and Eletta was well dressed.

01:25:57.500 --> 01:25:59.166
<i>Now come here</i>

01:26:02.208 --> 01:26:05.708
<i>And gently close your eyes</i>

01:26:07.875 --> 01:26:10.958
<i>You’ll see that the sadness will go away</i>

01:26:11.916 --> 01:26:15.375
<i>And the rest, who knows</i>
<i>It will come tomorrow</i>

01:26:17.666 --> 01:26:19.666
<i>I want to be with </i>you

01:26:21.708 --> 01:26:25.083
<i>Kiss your lips and tell you that</i>

01:26:27.000 --> 01:26:30.416
<i>In a time when everything passes</i>

01:26:31.416 --> 01:26:33.083
<i>Where everything changes</i>

01:26:33.625 --> 01:26:35.625
<i>We are still here</i>

01:26:38.416 --> 01:26:42.083
<i>And we don’t need words</i>

01:26:43.208 --> 01:26:48.666
<i>To explain what is hidden</i>
<i>Deep in our hearts</i>

01:26:50.000 --> 01:26:55.416
<i>But I will lift you up</i>
<i>Every time you fall</i>

01:26:55.916 --> 01:27:01.083
<i>And I will pick up your flowers</i>
<i>That you’ll lose on the street</i>

01:27:01.916 --> 01:27:06.666
<i>And I will follow your flight</i>
<i>Without ever interfering</i>

01:27:08.541 --> 01:27:14.083
<i>Because all I want is to be with </i>you

01:27:15.250 --> 01:27:20.375
<i>Without chains, to be with </i>you

01:28:00.708 --> 01:28:01.958
Get dressed.

01:29:10.416 --> 01:29:15.875
<i>The freedom</i>

01:29:23.666 --> 01:29:28.958
<i>Over my cruel fate</i>

01:29:30.125 --> 01:29:35.458
And sigh…

01:31:41.875 --> 01:31:43.500
<i>I would like</i>

01:31:45.166 --> 01:31:46.833
<i>To give you my word</i>

01:32:42.291 --> 01:32:43.541
<i>I would like</i>

01:32:45.708 --> 01:32:49.166
<i>To give you my word</i>
<i>To tell you, I can’t wait</i>

01:32:49.750 --> 01:32:51.666
<i>To forget everything</i>

01:32:52.333 --> 01:32:55.041
<i>I would like to tell you</i>
<i>That I have no voice</i>

01:32:55.125 --> 01:32:59.250
<i>So I don’t have to talk</i>
<i>That I can’t choose anymore</i>

01:32:59.333 --> 01:33:02.750
<i>I used to go out</i>
<i>With broken bones</i>

01:33:03.458 --> 01:33:06.875
<i>My mind was in love</i>
<i>But with abstract things</i>

01:33:07.458 --> 01:33:11.333
<i>Now I don’t know what to do</i>
<i>I don’t know where to go anymore</i>

01:33:11.416 --> 01:33:13.416
<i>I have to get used to </i>it

01:33:14.583 --> 01:33:18.458
<i>I was lost in a vortex</i>
<i>As if trapped at the edge</i>

01:33:18.541 --> 01:33:22.583
<i>I asked you for fairy tales</i>
<i>Like the sea of Atlantis</i>

01:33:22.666 --> 01:33:23.833
<i>I’m scared and I admit </i>it

01:33:24.583 --> 01:33:26.041
<i>I’ve been waiting for months</i>

01:33:26.625 --> 01:33:31.250
<i>Now I change direction</i>
<i>But I don’t change my intention</i>

01:33:31.583 --> 01:33:35.458
<i>I have nothing to say</i>
<i>I want to break free from the edge</i>

01:33:35.541 --> 01:33:39.625
<i>At least I try to understand</i>
<i>How much it hurts to leave</i>

01:33:39.708 --> 01:33:42.791
<i>I’ll be there waiting for you</i>
<i>Somewhere else in the world</i>

01:33:42.875 --> 01:33:47.125
<i>Now I change direction</i>
<i>But I don’t change my intention</i>

01:33:49.208 --> 01:33:52.958
<i>I’m just in a bigger hurry</i>
<i>With my hands in my pockets</i>

01:33:53.041 --> 01:33:55.791
<i>And your keys always in my purse</i>
<i>Come </i>on

01:33:57.166 --> 01:33:59.250
<i>Don’t turn your back this time either</i>

01:33:59.333 --> 01:34:03.125
<i>I see everything in your eyes</i>
<i>I need nothing more</i>

01:34:03.208 --> 01:34:07.416
<i>I keep asking myself</i>
<i>If I’m the one who’s wrong</i>

01:34:07.916 --> 01:34:11.250
<i>If I wasted time</i>
<i>And didn’t give you my </i>all

01:34:12.000 --> 01:34:15.875
<i>But now I know what to do</i>
<i>I know where to </i>go

01:34:16.083 --> 01:34:18.041
<i>I have to get used to </i>it

01:34:19.083 --> 01:34:23.041
<i>I was lost in a vortex</i>
<i>As if trapped at the edge</i>

01:34:23.125 --> 01:34:26.958
<i>I asked you for fairy tales</i>
<i>Like the sea of Atlantis</i>

01:34:27.041 --> 01:34:28.416
<i>I’m scared and I admit </i>it

01:34:29.083 --> 01:34:30.416
